description:
&lt;p&gt;Double shifts, night shifts, working all weekend? Sorry, we don’t offer any of these at SpaMedica…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What we do offer are friendly teams, first-class hospitals and time for you to give all your focus and attention to each one of your patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SpaMedica knows work/life balance is vital for our nurses and so we work 4-day shifts and only ‘1 in 4’ weekends. And, you’ll get a great salary plus two bonuses per year, for, hopefully, doing a job you love.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You may not have heard of SpaMedica, so it’s important to understand who we are. Please visit our website and/or read some of our fantastic reviews on NHS UK – where we now have over 900 5-star ratings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here’s a little about us to begin with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are privileged to be able to support the tens of thousands of NHS patients that come to SpaMedica each year.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are dedicated to reducing NHS waiting times for cataract surgery, YAG capsulotomy and AMD treatments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are proud to deliver excellent care and support thousands of patients to achieve better vision – our outcomes are some of the best in the UK, with low complication rates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We want our staff to enjoy coming to work and provide a friendly and supportive environment for you to work in.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In 2018 we became the largest provider of NHS cataract surgery – 24.000+ surgeries per annum.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have 15 hospitals and will be opening 7 new hospitals over the next 12 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our nurses’ package includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some of the best salary bandings in healthcare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuous training and development programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus 1 – June - Up to 5% individual performance related bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus 2 – February - hospital/company related bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Annual pay reviews and increases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4-day shifts – no evenings and 1 in 4 weekends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days holiday (33 days including bank holidays)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be considered for this role you will hold a current NMC/HCPC registration and have at least 12 months post-registration experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will be predominantly based in Bristol with travel to other sites required on occasion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please call us for an informal chat if you’d like to find out more about working at SpaMedica. Or if you’re interested in this role, please apply now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/p&gt;
